Warehouse Team Leader (WTL)
Responsibilities
Managing end to end warehouse operations from good receiving, storage management, good dispatching, stock control and warehouse daily operationEnsure that all process and transactions are conducted in respect to the Standard Operating ProcedureResponsible for stock accuracy and to ensure all transactions are executed timely and accurately in the system with respect to company regulations and compliance.Ensure workplace health and safety requirement are met and take responsibility for the security of the building and the stockEnsure KPI targets are achieved and leading the team for continuous improvement  Requirements :Diploma or Bachelor Degree (D3 or S1) in Mechanical or Industrial Engineering.Minimum 5 years experiences in related field and will be advantage in industrial goods (Supervisory Level).Working knowledge in warehouse management systemHaving knowledge in Logistic IT System (SAP/ ERP), warehousing, and distribution or transport system.High level to operate computer: Ms. Office  Please send your resume, not more than 2 weeks from nowErita SitumorangPT Spirax Sarco Indonesia, Kawasan Infinia Park Blok C99, Jl. Dr. Saharjo No.45, Manggarai, Tebet,Jakarta Selatan, 12850Email: Erita.Situmorang@id.spiraxsarco.com
